   Liu, Chang-Qiu; Niu, Yang; Peng, De-Li; Sun, Hang, Chinese Acad Sci, Kunming Inst Bot, Key Lab Plant Divers \& Biogeog East Asia, Kunming 650201, Yunnan, Peoples R China.},
