   Gemeda, Tolera Kumsa; Yang, Huipeng; Huang, Jiaxing; Wu, Jie, Chinese Acad Agr Sci, Inst Apicultural Res, Minist Agr, Key Lab Insect Pollinator Biol, Beijing 100093, Peoples R China.
