   Meyer, Susan E., US Forest Serv, Rocky Mt Res Stn, Shrub Sci Lab, Provo, UT 84606 USA.
   Pendleton, Burton K., US Forest Serv, Rocky Mt Res Stn, Albuquerque, NM 87102 USA.},
